  <body>
    <div id="root"><div class="bg-slate-200 min-h-screen py-4 print:p-0 print:bg-white font-sans text-slate-900"><style>
          @media print {
            @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
            body { -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; }
            .no-print { display: none !important; }
            .page-container { 
              width: 210mm;
              height: 297mm;
              margin: 0 !important;
              padding: 0 !important;
              shadow: none !important;
              display: flex !important;
              flex-direction: row !important;
            }
          }
        </style><div class="max-w-[950px] mx-auto bg-white shadow-2xl flex flex-col md:flex-row page-container overflow-hidden"><aside class="w-full md:w-[32%] bg-[#F1F5F9] p-8 border-r border-slate-300 flex flex-col print:h-full"><div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8"><div class="w-44 h-44 bg-slate-300 border-[5px] border-white shadow-lg overflow-hidden rounded-full mb-5"><img alt="Profil" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="./mon_files/ma-photo.jpg"></div><h1 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#004b87] text-center leading-none uppercase tracking-tighter">MOHAMED IDRISS NANA</h1><p class="text-[11px] text-slate-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mt-3 text-center border-t border-[#004b87]/20 pt-2">Étudiant en Informatique - UM6P</p></div><div class="space-y-8 flex-grow"><section><h2 class="text-[#004b87] font-black border-b-2 border-[#004b87] pb-1 mb-3 uppercase text-[11px] tracking-widest">Contact</h2><ul class="text-[12px] space-y-3 text-slate-700 font-bold"><li>📍 Ben Guerir, Maroc</li><li>📞 +212 775198692</li><li>📧 nanaidriss70@gmail.com</li><li class="truncate underline text-[10px]">linkedin.com/in/mohamed-nana</li><li class="underline text-[10px]">github.com/momo226-code</li></ul></section><section><h2 class="text-[#004b87] font-black border-b-2 border-[#004b87] pb-1 mb-3 uppercase text-[11px] tracking-widest">Expertise</h2><div class="space-y-4 text-[12px]"><div><p class="font-black text-slate-900 uppercase text-[10px] mb-1">Data &amp; Architecture</p><p class="text-slate-700 italic font-medium leading-relaxed">SQL (MySQL), NoSQL (MongoDB), Python, C/C++, Linux &amp; Docker</p></div><div><p class="font-black text-slate-900 uppercase text-[10px] mb-1">Développement Web</p><p class="text-slate-700 italic font-medium leading-relaxed">React, Vue.js (Nuxt.js), Node.js, Flask, Tailwind CSS</p></div></div></section><section><h2 class="text-[#004b87] font-black border-b-2 border-[#004b87] pb-1 mb-3 uppercase text-[11px] tracking-widest">Compétences</h2><ul class="text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-700 space-y-2 uppercase italic"><li>• Leadership &amp; Gestion d'équipe</li><li>• Agilité &amp; Collaboration</li><li>• Résolution de problèmes complexes</li></ul></section><section><h2 class="text-[#004b87] font-black border-b-2 border-[#004b87] pb-1 mb-3 uppercase text-[11px] tracking-widest">Langues</h2><div class="text-[12px] font-bold space-y-2"><div class="flex justify-between"><span>Français</span><span class="text-[#004b87]">Maternel</span></div><div class="flex justify-between"><span>Anglais</span><span class="text-[#004b87]">Niveau B2</span></div></div></section><section><h2 class="text-[#004b87] font-black border-b-2 border-[#004b87] pb-1 mb-3 uppercase text-[11px] tracking-widest">Distinctions</h2><ul class="text-[11px] space-y-3 text-slate-700 font-bold italic"><li>🏆 2e Prix Olympiades Nationales de Maths (Lycée, 2022)</li><li>🏅 Lauréat Fondation Orange Burkina (2023)</li><li>🏅 2e Prix Olympiades Maths (Collège, 2019)</li></ul></section></div></aside><main class="w-full md:w-[68%] p-10 print:p-9 flex flex-col bg-white"><div class="bg-[#004b87] text-white p-7 rounded-br-[35px] mb-8 shadow-md"><h2 class="text-lg font-black uppercase italic mb-2 tracking-tight">Candidature : Stage PFA</h2><p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed font-bold opacity-95">Étudiant passionné par l'ingénierie logicielle et la donnée. Recherche d'un stage technique de 2 mois (Juillet-Août 2026) pour contribuer à la digitalisation des flux SI chez Vinci Energies.</p></div><section class="mb-10 break-inside-avoid"><h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-vinci uppercase tracking-tighter mb-8 border-l-[8px] border-vinci pl-4">Parcours Professionnel</h2><div class="flex gap-6 items-start"><div class="w-20 h-20 flex-shrink-0 bg-white border-2 border-slate-100 p-2 rounded-lg shadow-sm"><img alt="Logo AEBM" class="w-full h-full object-contain" src="./mon_files/aebm.jpg"></div><div class="flex-1"><div class="flex justify-between items-baseline"><h3 class="font-black text-[18px] text-slate-900 uppercase">Chargé Académique et Culturel | AEBM</h3><span class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-500 italic bg-slate-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">2024-2025</span></div><ul class="text-[15px] text-slate-700 mt-4 space-y-3 list-disc ml-5 font-medium leading-relaxed italic"><li>Organisation des "Cultural Days-UM6P" (Gestion logistique et coordination de projets à grande échelle).</li><li>Pilotage de webinaires sur l'insertion professionnelle et l'entrepreneuriat.</li><li>Encadrement de workshops techniques et coordination d'équipes de bénévoles.</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="mb-8"><h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#004b87] uppercase mb-5 border-l-[6px] border-[#004b87] pl-3">Réalisations &amp; Ingénierie</h2><div class="space-y-6"><div class="relative p-5 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200"><div class="absolute -top-3 right-4 flex gap-2"><span class="bg-yellow-500 text-white text-[8px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-tighter">SOUTENU PAR MASTERCARD FOUNDATION</span><span class="bg-[#004b87] text-white text-[8px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase"> EN COURS</span></div><div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-1"><h3 class="font-black text-[16px] text-slate-900 uppercase">Ventura : Marketplace SI (Stack MERN)</h3><span class="text-[9px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest text-right">React.js / MongoDB</span></div><p class="text-[13px] text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-medium mt-2 italic">Conception d'une plateforme sécurisée d'échanges de services à l'UM6P. Intégration d'un système d'annonces temps réel avec base de données NoSQL (MongoDB) et authentification JWT.</p></div><div class="pl-5 border-l-4 border-slate-200 py-1"><div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-1"><h3 class="font-black text-[15px] text-slate-900 uppercase">Spotify Clone - Streaming Audio</h3><span class="text-[9px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest text-right">Nuxt.js / Vue.js</span></div><p class="text-[13px] text-slate-700 font-medium italic">Reproduction haute fidélité de l'interface Spotify. Gestion d'états réactifs (Pinia), navigation fluide (SSR) et lecture audio synchronisée.</p></div><div class="pl-5 border-l-4 border-slate-200 py-1"><div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-1"><h3 class="font-black text-[15px] text-slate-900 uppercase">Gestion Hospitalière MNHS</h3><span class="text-[9px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest text-right">Flask / MySQL</span></div><p class="text-[13px] text-slate-700 font-medium italic">Digitalisation des stocks critiques et analyse de données cliniques via Python. Modélisation SQL optimisée pour le suivi des performances.</p></div></div></section><section class="mt-auto pt-4 border-t-2 border-slate-100"><h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#004b87] uppercase mb-5 border-l-[6px] border-[#004b87] pl-3">Formation &amp; Certifications</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div><h3 class="font-black text-[15px] text-slate-900 uppercase leading-tight">College of Computing – UM6P</h3><p class="text-[12px] text-[#004b87] font-black uppercase mt-1">Cycle Ingénieur Informatique</p><p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-bold italic mt-1 leading-tight">Classe Préparatoire Intégrée</p><p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold italic">2023 - Présent | Ben Guerir, Maroc</p></div><div><h3 class="font-black text-[13px] text-slate-900 uppercase leading-tight">Lycée WendKonta</h3><p class="text-[11px] text-slate-700 font-bold italic mt-0.5">Baccalauréat D (Major de Promotion)</p></div></div><div class="text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-600 space-y-2 bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-100"><p class="text-[#004b87] uppercase text-[9px] mb-2 tracking-widest border-b border-[#004b87]/20 pb-1 font-black">Validations Techniques</p><p>• Introduction to Cybersecurity (Cisco)</p><p>• Introduction to Prompt Engineering (Simplilearn)</p><p>• Introduction to Cloud Computing (Simplilearn)</p></div></div></section></main></div><button class="no-print fixed bottom-8 right-8 bg-[#004b87] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full shadow-2xl font-black flex items-center gap-2 hover:scale-105 transition-all z-50"><span>🖨️</span> GÉNÉRER LE PDF VINCI</button></div></div>
